quran[8{c,v,t}:
7,74,"yaad karo woh waqt jab Allah ne qoum Aad ke baad tumhe is ka janasheen banaya aur tum ko zameen mein yeh manzilat bakhsh ke tum uss ke hamwar mahdanon mein aliiiii shaan mehal banatay aur is ke pahoron ko makanaat ki shakal mein tarashtain ho pas is ki qudrat ke karishmo se ghaafil nah ho jao aur zameen mein fasaad barpaa nah karo """
7,75,"uss ki qoum ke sardaro ne jo barray banay hue thay, kamzor tabqa ke unn logon se jo imaan le aeye thay kaha"" kya tum waqai yeh jantay ho ke saleh apne rab ka paighambar hai ?"" unhon ne jawab diya"" be shak jis pegham ke sath woh bheja gaya hai ussay hum mantay hain """
7,76,"unn buraiee ke mdayon ne kaha jis cheez ko tum ne maana hai hum is ke munkir hain """
7,77,"phir unhon ne is oontni ko maar dala aur poooray tamarad ke sath apne rab ke hukum ki khilaaf warzi kar guzray, aur saleh se keh diya ke le aa woh azaab jis ki to hamein dhamki deta hai agar to waqai payghambaroon mein se hai"
7,78,aakhir ka ray aik dhula dainay wali aafat ne unhen aa liya aur woh apne gharon mein avndhe parre ke parre reh gay
7,79,"aur saleh yeh kehta howa un ki bustiyon se nikal gaya ke"" ae meri qoum, mein ne apne rab ka pegham tujhe pouncha diya aur mein ne teri bohat kher khawahi ki, magar mein kya karoon ke tujhe apne kher khuwa pasand hi nahi hain """
7,80,"aur loot ko hum ne paighambar bana kar bheja, phir yaad karo jab uss ne apni qoum se kaha"" kya tum aisay be haya ho gay ho, ke woh fehash kaam karte ho jo tum se pehlay duniya mein kisi ne nahi kya ?"
7,81,"tum aurton ko chore kar mardon se apni khwahish poori karte ho haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum bilkul hi hadd se guzar jaane walay log ho """
